@baseUrl = http://localhost:8005/api

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/health

### 2. Database Statistics & TMDB Enrichment Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/stats

### 3. User Registration
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "developer",
  "email": "dev@example.com",
  "password": "strongpassword123"
}

### 4. User Login (Obtain Access Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=developer&password=strongpassword123

### 5. Get Current Authenticated Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 6. Search Movies (returns enriched TMDB data: posters, overview, cast)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?q=Toy Story

### 7. Get Single Movie Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1

### 8. Submit Movie Ratings (rate a few movies to build taste profile)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 1,
  "rating": 5.0
}

### 9. Rate another movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 356,
  "rating": 4.5
}

### 10. Rate another movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 318,
  "rating": 5.0
}

### 11. Get Rating History
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings/history
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 12. Get Personalized Hybrid Recommendations (with TMDB poster URLs, cast, overview)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 13. Get Similar Movies (Content-Based)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1/similar?method=content&limit=5

### 14. Get System Metrics (RMSE, NDCG, Coverage, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/metrics

### 15. Trigger TMDB Enrichment (requires TMDB_API_KEY in .env)
# Enriches movie posters, overviews, cast, directors from TMDB API
# Use limit parameter to enrich in batches: ?limit=500
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/enrich

### 16. Trigger Model Retraining
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/train
